0.1.name: wordpress/feed-key
0.1.description:
Feed Key adds a 32bit (or 40bit) key for each of your users, creating a unique feed url for every registered on user the site. This allows you to restrict you feeds to registered users only.

Feed Key is a side project of another of my plugins Members Only. It has some expanded option on how the Feed Keys are generated. You don't need to use both plugins.
